# Belaluur

Description: Female. Missing an ear and wears a fine leather cloak. She is jovial by nature but is nevertheless a shrewd bargainer and ruthless operator.
Location: Sanctuary, Talenta Plains
Mannerisms: Belaluur glances warily over her shoulder when she talks.
Motivation: Greed, Wealth
Quote / Flavor: “If I had a crown for every time someone said that to me, I’d be richer than the Queen of Aundair.”
Race: Goblin
Role: Information broker, Salvage
Status: Alive